OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud in north soon
OL,6,Fclearing during the morning with
OL,7,Fbright and sunny spells developing.
OL,8,FTemperatures down a bit, especially in
OL,9,Fnorthwest, but still warm or very warm
OL,10,Fin the sunshine. Light northwesterly
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine warm sunny evening in
OL,14,Fall areas then a dry night with some
OL,15,Flong clear spells. Clouding over over
OL,16,Fby morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FA dry day. A rather cloudy
OL,19,Fstart then the cloud breaking up to
OL,20,Fallow some sunny spells again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
