OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods on Sunday, warm
OL,7,Fwith light winds. More cloud at times
OL,8,Fon Monday and Tuesday but still dry
OL,9,Fwiith some sunny intervals.
